data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!   NEED SPACE? THIS 2,496 S.F. ELEVATED POOL HOME COULD BE THE ONE FOR YOU! CUSTOM FEATURES INCLUDE A FIREPLACE IN THE FAMILY ROOM, VAULTED CEILINGS, SPLIT BEDROOMS & MUCH MORE. THE OVER-SIZED EAT-IN-KITCHEN HAS ABUNDANT CABINET SPACE, SOLID SURFACE COUNTERTOPS PLUS A GAS RANGE FOR THE GOURMET CHEF. IF ENTERTAINING IS IMPORTANT, A FORMAL LIVING ROOM & ADJACENT FORMAL DINING ROOM ADD AMBIANCE. YOU & YOUR GUESTS WILL APPRECIATE THE SCREENED & ENCLOSED LANAI & POOL AREA. THIS LOVELY HOME IS LOCATED ON A CORNER LOT WITH A CIRCULAR DRIVE. ADDITIONAL PARKING WITH GARAGE ACCESS IS ON THE SIDE. THE CENTRAL AIR CONDITIONING-HEAT WERE REPLACED IN 2019, EXTERIOR PAINTING, STUCCO WORK & WINDOW REPAIRS WERE COMPLETED IN 2022. THE SELLER HAS A TERMINIX CONTRACT & IS OFFERING A ONE YEAR BASIC HOME OWNER WARRANTY. FOR ADDITIONAL VALUE, A $3,000 HIGH IMPACT ENTRY DOOR HAS BEEN INSTALLED. GULF HARBORS IS A WONDERFUL COMMUNITY WITH AN OPTIONAL BEACH CLUB MEMBERSHIP @ $180.00 YEARLY. CENTRALLY LOCATED IN FLORIDA, APPROXIMATELY ONE HOUR TO TAMPA INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT, PROFESSIONAL SPORTING EVENTS, TOURIST ATTRACTIONS, FINE DINING & BEACHES.
